{"id":615655,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【麻辣总局】巴丢草-谁是武则天-谁是四个瓜/","date":"2019-08-17T05:15:32Z","modified":"2019-08-17T05:21:58Z","title":"【麻辣总局】巴丢草 | 谁是武则天 谁是四个瓜","content":"<p>香港近月有关《逃犯条例》修订引发的示威浪潮持续。多间大型香港公司和地产发展商先后在当地报章刊登广告，讉责示威者的暴力。其中，退休商人李嘉诚周五（8月16日）在多份报章刊登广告，同样呼吁要停止暴力，却引起外界不同解读。（BBC）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336852_img_5201.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615657\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336852_img_5201.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336852_img_5201.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336852_img_5201-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336858_img_5205.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615658\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336858_img_5205.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336858_img_5205.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/108336858_img_5205-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@badiucao：My cartoon echoing with Ka-shing Li‘s HK headline AD poem about melons. It is metaphor for Prince Zhang became crown prince in 675 but soon fell out of favor with Empress Wu, his mother. In 680, Wu forced him to suicide.黄台之瓜，何堪再摘 —— 李嘉诚  谁是武则天，谁是四个瓜，懂？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ECDskbaU0AAoV44.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615656\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ECDskbaU0AAoV44.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"621\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ECDskbaU0AAoV44.jpg 725w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ECDskbaU0AAoV44-242x300.jpg 242w\" sizes=\"(max-widt